```var $input = $('.hs_submit input',$this);
							var submitVal = $input.val();
							var element = $input[0].outerHTML.replace('&lt;input','&lt;button')+'&lt;/button&gt;';
							var $button = $(element);
							$input.replaceWith($button);
							$button.html(submitVal+'&lt;i class="material-icons"&gt;chevron_right&lt;/i&gt;');```
I used the above code to add a material design icon chevron to the submit button
